1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Why does MPN matter in PCBA BOM sourcing?

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:08,000
MPN means manufacturer part number. It identifies the exact component.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:14,000
Without clear MPNs, suppliers may quote different brands, packages, or specifications.

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Clear BOM data reduces sourcing risk, replacement confusion, and quotation delays.

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:28,000
A useful BOM includes MPN, quantity, package, reference designator, and acceptable alternatives.

6
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:35,000
For turnkey PCBA, send Gerber, BOM, quantity, and testing requirements for review.

7
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:38,000
Learn more at huitaipcb.com/bom-sourcing-pcb-assembly
